                                'Xix' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Xix' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where the goal is to connect
diagonally 3 shapes together. Also, any series of connected shapes
must include at least one 'X' shape. If there are 2 'X' shapes in
any series and/or if all shapes in a series are of the same colour,
the better it is...

  Have fun!

